[[File:Wizard Sinina chathead.png|left]]
'''Wizard Sinina''' sells [[mystic robes]] and other mystic equipment in the [[Wizards' Guild]] through the [[Magic Guild Store - Mystic Robes|mystic robes store]]. He is located on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of the guild, next to [[Wizard Akutha]].

If a player has achieved 99 [[Magic]], they can purchase a [[magic cape]] and its respective hood from him for 99,000 coins.

Level 66 [[Magic]] is required to access the Wizards' Guild, where Wizard Sinina resides.

